    </note>
    <note caller="[j]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[j]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">Paul determined by the Spirit</char>…Lit: <char style="it">Paul put himself by the Spirit</char>.
        The word <char style="it">put </char>when<char style="it"> </char>used concerning one’s heart is an expression.
        This expression appears in 5:2 also.</char>
